Welcome to Bejeweled Fans!
Please check the pinned message in welcome to view the rules of the server.
If you have any queries for it, feel free to ask a someone from Hypercube to Darksphere ranks to help you around.
If you came here looking for 'Dijeweled' , click here #dijeweled and check pins.
If you came here looking for the obsolete 'Dijeweled Multiplayer' or to find players to play in Dijeweled Remaster, click here #multiplayer-lobby and check pins.
Be sure to stick around, you never know what you might come across that peaks your interest.
